raw_data.title: Project Manager
raw_data.description: Advanced level of technical subject matter expertise as well as functioning within an experienced level of leadership. Responsibilities include oversight of large scope projects, both analog and IP while effectively managing a large team of installation techs while being responsible for time, financial resources and ensuring that quality standards are met. Additional areas of responsibility include product training and orientation to the end user.
